data.value: The Hyundai Creta has 2 Diesel Engine and 1 Petrol Engine on offer. The Diesel engine is 1396 cc and 1582 cc while the Petrol engine is 1591 cc. It is available with the Manual and Automatic transmission.

data.name: label5.Text
data.value: The Maruti Ciaz has 2 Diesel Engine and 1 Petrol Engine on offer. The Diesel engine is 1248 cc and 1498 cc while the Petrol engine is 1462 cc. It is available with the Manual and Automatic transmission. Depending upon the variant and fuel type the Ciaz has a mileage of 20.28 to 28.09 kmpl.

data.name: label6.Text
data.value: The Maruti Alto has 2 Petrol Engine and 1 CNG Engine on offer. The Petrol engine is 796 cc and 1061 cc while the CNG engine is 796 cc. It is available with the transmission. Depending upon the variant and fuel type the Alto has a mileage of 18.9 kmpl to 26.83 km/kg.

data.name: label8.Text
data.value: Jeep offers the Compass with the choice of two engines, one petrol and one diesel. The petrol engine is a 1.4-litre turbo-petrol that makes 163PS/250Nm whereas the diesel engine is a 2.0-litre unit that churns out 173PS/350Nm. The manual transmission option for both engines is a 6-speed gearbox.
